This paper deals with the integration of ontology languages and rule paradigms, which is a common topic in artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and databases (cs.DB). The paper also discusses the use of logic programming and tabled rule evaluation, which are relevant to programming languages (cs.PL) and software engineering (cs.SE). Finally, the paper focuses on the semantics of the knowledge base, which is a topic in logic (cs.LO).
